{"timestamp": "2025-12-05 02:12:20.533387", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission summary:\n- Anomaly detected: Yes\n- Faulty device(s): spine_router_0_1\n- Root cause: bgp_blackhole_route_leak\n\nDetails:\nA more-specific tenant route 10.0.1.0/25 was misconfigured on spine_router_0_1 (loopback and advertised via BGP). This leaked a blackhole route into the fabric, hijacking traffic for 10.0.1.0–10.0.1.127 and causing HTTP failures to web0.pod0 despite DNS and ICMP success.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2068, "output_tokens": 121, "total_tokens": 2189, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1920}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
